headline.main: Warrant Shows Police Have Suspects in Death of 9-Year-Old
headline.print_headline: Warrant Shows Police Have Suspects in Death of 9-Year-Old

lead_paragraph: A recently unsealed search warrant shows police have suspects in the fatal shooting of a 9-year-old Milwaukee girl last year, but authorities are still seeking evidence to bring charges in her death.
